name: Receiving an item by providing the item barcode

testSteps.description: Example: {ASN=ASN10001, item barcode=ITEM001, quantity=12, received qty=12}

children.description: Given User is on the RF screen
When User enter the "ASN10001" in the ASN field
Then User needs to enter the item details
When User enter the "ITEM001"
And User move to the next screen
Then User is requested to enter the item quantity
When User enter the quanity as "12"
Then the received quanity is incremented with the "12"
